13596,"6875 Sand Lake Rd, Orlando, FL 32819, United States",28.4503866,-81.4714142,"19,671",3 months ago,Fantastic restaurant. You must visit when in Orlando. The service was good. The wait time for the premium menu items was reasonable. It was very clean and the staff was exceptional.,5 stars,positive,,positive
13597,"6875 Sand Lake Rd, Orlando, FL 32819, United States",28.4503866,-81.4714142,"19,671",2 weeks ago,"The food was quality but service took a while.

