13694,"6875 Sand Lake Rd, Orlando, FL 32819, United States",28.4503866,-81.4714142,"19,671",2 months ago,"My kids wanted to check this McDonald���������������������������s location.. ���������������������������largest McDonald���������������������������s��������������������������� but they forgot to add, slowest service ever in the fast food industry in their description. We waited 55 minutes for our order. The staff was calm & patient despite all of the unhappy people who were waited for almost an hour for their orders as well. To whomever is running this location, please get your staff the proper help that they need. I�",2 stars,negative,,negative
