13745,"6875 Sand Lake Rd, Orlando, FL 32819, United States",28.4503866,-81.4714142,"19,671",2 days ago,"Today we had the opportunity to go to such a well-known McDonald's, the truth is that the place is very nice, but in terms of the attention and organization it was terrible, half of my order was missing and although I went to tell them that it was wrong, they did not pay attention to me. So many employees so they can't help me in my order. My children were very excited to go to the play place but their air conditioning did not work and it was unbearably hot. They should pay a little attention to those flaws. Thank you",2 stars,negative,,negative
